 elements that define the restaurant’s identity include CNC-milled woodwork, woven rope ceilings, patterned terrazzo flooring, brass inlays, and bespoke lighting fixtures. Because design, prototyping, and fabrication all happened under one roof, the transition from concept to construction was both efficient and precise, eliminating the gaps that often occur between designers and contractors.</p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">The result of Ipanema is an interior that feels immersive, rhythmic, and distinctly Brazilian, yet rooted in Manhattan’s modern energy. By uniting design, fabrication, and construction under one roof, Bolt Builds delivered a hospitality project that embodies a sensory paradise while evoking the fluid beauty of the Amazon River.</p></div><div class="z-10 relative right-0 left-0 h-12 pt-10"><div class="z-10 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 bottom-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-white from-70% to-transparent transition-opacity duration-300 opacity-100"></div><button type="button" aria-label="Read More" class="relative z-20 hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity pt-4"><p class="text-current font-body text-md font-bold">Read More</p></button></div></div></div></div><div class="col-start-1 md:col-start-3 md:col-end-11 col-end-13 lg:col-start-7 lg:col-end-12 xl:col-end-11"><div role="button" class="cursor-zoom-in hover:opacity-75 transition-opacity"><img src="https://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2F2bf86d73620ef1b8437d706199b66773aa9646f6-2053x2732.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" srcSet="https://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2F2bf86d73620ef1b8437d706199b66773aa9646f6-2053x2732.jpg&w=3840&q=75amp;q=75 1x" alt="" width="2053" height="2732" class="w-full h-full" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 50vw, 33vw"/></div></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-unit px-unit pb-unit md:pb-24"><div class="col-start-1 col-span-6