here modern brewery design meets cultural craftsmanship. Bolt Builds, a Brooklyn-based design, build and fabrication studio reimagined this expansive restaurant by drawing inspiration from the natural landscape and infusing the interiors with outdoor materials and organic geometries."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"c4bad10bd751","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"d06386f365310","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"From the moment guests arrive, they are greeted by bold architectural gestures, angular thresholds, soaring ceilings, and a dramatic two-sided staircase that anchors the space and creates multiple layers of experience. The interiors combine concrete, brick, teak wood, and lush greenery with vivid colors and playful patterns, resulting in a setting that feels deeply rooted in place. To ensure authenticity, Bolt Builds worked closely with skilled local artisans and used locally sourced materials from Bangalore, weaving handmade textures and bespoke details into the design."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"84be3e8ea6a6","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"fd5527c61de60","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"The result is a space that harmonizes craft, culture, and innovation into a full-circle experience. By merging local materiality with international design sensibilities, The Druid Garden establishes itself as one of the most distinctive brewery and restaurant interiors in Bangalore, showcasing how Bolt Builds delivers hospitality spaces that balance durability, beauty, and immersive atmosphere."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"descriptionPlaintext":"The Druid Garden | Contemporary Restaurant Design in Bangalore by Bolt Builds\n\nInspired by nature and the garden, The Druid Garden in Bangalore, India, is a striking 23,000 SF hospitality project where modern brewery design meets cultural craftsmanship. Bolt Builds, a Brooklyn-based design, build and fabrication studio reimagined this expansive restaurant by drawing inspiration from the natural landscape and infusing the interiors with outdoor materials and organic geometries.\n\nFrom the moment guests arrive, they are greeted by bold architectural gestures, angular thresholds, soaring ceilings, and a dramatic two-sided staircase that anchors the space and creates multiple layers of experience. The interiors combine concrete, brick, teak wood, and lush greenery with vivid colors and playful patterns, resulting in a setting that feels deeply rooted in place. To ensure authenticity, Bolt Builds worked closely with skilled local artisans and used locally sourced materials from Bangalore, weaving handmade textures and bespoke details into the design.\n\nThe result is a space that harmonizes craft, culture, and innovation into a full-circle experience. By merging local materiality with international design sensibilities, The Druid Garden establishes itself as one of the most distinctive brewery and restaurant interiors in Bangalore, showcasing how Bolt Builds delivers hospitality spaces that balance durability, beauty, and immersive atmosphere.","featuredImage":{"_key":null,"_type":"image","asset":{"_id":"image-7afc0d93eeebbf13527aaf7858a1e44eb1815112-8564x5709-jpg","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","description":null,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"aspectRatio":1.5000875810124366,"height":5709,"width":8564},"lqip":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"tags":["Bar Design NYC","Bolt","Bolt Builds","Bolt Builds NYC","Bolt Builds New York City","Bolt Design NYC","Bolt New York City","Boutique Design Agency New York","Custom Interior Design New York","Custom millwork NYC","Elegant Hospitality Interiors NYC","High-End Bar Design NYC","High-End Interior Design Agency NYC","High-End Retail Design New York","High-end Millwork NYC","Hospitality","Hospitality Interior Design New York","Innovative Hospitality Solutions New York","Luxery Millwork NYC","Luxury Bar Design NYC","Luxury Hospitality Consultants NYC","Luxury Millwork NYC","NYC Residential Interior Designers","New York","New